==Indonesian==

===Verb===
====Intransitive====
'''datang'''

# to [[come]]
#* [[Minggu]] [[yang]] '''datang''' [[saya]] [[akan]] [[membeli]] [[buku]] [[itu]].
#* Next week I am going to buy that book. 
# to [[arrive]]
#* [[Saya]] '''datang''' [[terlambat]].
#* I arrived late.

[[Category:Indonesian language]][[Category:Indonesian verbs]]

====Usage notes====
* "[[Selamat]] '''datang'''" is a [[greeting]] that means "[[welcome]]".

